'''雷蒙·威廉·沙爾克'''（{{lang-en|Raymond William Schalk}}，{{bd|1892年|8月12日|1970年|5月19日|}}），綽號「耶弗他」，為美國職棒大聯盟的捕手。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference">{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/schalra01.shtml |title=Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2021-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517004055/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/schalra01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>職業生涯幾乎都效力於芝加哥白襪，<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=schalra01 |title=Ray Schalk at Baseball Almanac |publisher=Baseball Almanac |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2021-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424170921/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=schalra01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後一年則待在紐約巨人。沙爾克被譽為是當時最強的防守型捕手，<ref name="Ray Schalk Takes Job With Cubs">{{cite news |title=Ray Schalk Takes Job With Cubs |agency=Associated Press |work=St. Petersburg Times |date=6 June 1944 |access-date=12 January 2011 |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MKFPAAAAIBAJ&pg=4272,7196569&dq=ray+schalk&hl=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=In Catching, The White Sox Lead |work=The Crawfordsville Review |page=7 |date=2 October 1917 |access-date=15 January 2011 |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=AIwnAAAAIBAJ&pg=2419,3146697&dq=ray+schalk&hl=en}}</ref>也是大聯盟少見的敏捷型捕手。<ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk">{{cite web |url=http://bioproj.sabr.org/bioproj.cfm?a=v&v=l&bid=1798&pid=12561 |title=The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk |author=Stevens, Brian |publisher=Society for American Baseball Research |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604205034/http://bioproj.sabr.org/bioproj.cfm?a=v&v=l&bid=1798&pid=12561 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1955年，沙爾克入選名人堂。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://baseballhall.org/hof/schalk-ray |title=Ray Schalk at the Baseball Hall of Fame |publisher=baseballhall.org |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2010-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100918071443/http://baseballhall.org/hof/schalk-ray |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==職業生涯==
1912年8月11日，沙爾克在他滿20歲生日前一天登上大聯盟。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/>這年他的打擊率為2成86，而防守部分更是讓總教練印象深刻。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/><ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk"/>因此他在隔年取代Billy Sullivan成為球隊的先發捕手。<ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1913-fielding-leaders.shtml |title=1913 American League Fielding Leaders |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2021-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429182416/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1913-fielding-leaders.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

沙爾克只有175公分高，以大聯盟選手來說身形相對瘦小。但是嬌小的身軀讓他比其他捕手更加靈活，更能像內野手一樣迅速的接球。<ref name="Slim Catchers Replace Big Men In Majors">{{cite news |title=Slim Catchers Replace Big Men In Majors |work=The Pittsburgh Gazette Times |page=8 |date=6 August 1916 |access-date=15 January 2011 |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1HtIAAAAIBAJ&pg=5215,5839392&dq=ray+schalk&hl=en}}</ref>

1914年，沙爾克的打擊率為2成70。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/>儘管球隊戰績不佳，他仍在MVP票選中拿下第六名。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1914.shtml#ALmvp |title=1914 American League Most Valuable Player Award voting |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2009-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130064549/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1914.shtml#ALmvp |dead-url=no }}</ref>1915年，雖然打擊率稍微下滑到2成66，不過他的防守數據比起去年又更加進步。1916年，沙爾克達成30次盜壘成功。不僅寫下生涯新高，這項捕手盜壘紀錄還高懸66年才被打破。白襪隊最後以2場勝差輸給紅襪，無緣拿下美聯冠軍。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1916.shtml |title=1916 American League standings |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2021-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322131756/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1916.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>但是沙爾克靠著他優異的配球能力，讓球隊的團隊防禦率排在美聯最佳。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1916.shtml#teams_standard_pitching::none |title=1916 American League pitching statistics |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2021-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322131756/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1916.shtml#teams_standard_pitching::none |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1917年，沙爾克的打擊率來到生涯新低的2成26，不過上壘率卻有3成31。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/>這年白襪成功闖進世界大賽，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1917.shtml |title=1917 American League standings |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308092859/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1917.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>並在世界大賽上擊敗巨人拿下冠軍。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1917_WS.shtml |title=1917 World Series |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422140719/http://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1917_WS.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1918年，沙爾克的打擊率掉到2成19，白襪隊僅拿下美聯第六名。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/>不過隔年他的打擊率回到2成82，球隊再次挺進世界大賽。然而，白襪隊在這年世界大賽上放水輸給紅人，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.1919blacksox.com/story.htm |title=The Black Sox |publisher=1919blacksox.com |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2020-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105231830/http://www.1919blacksox.com/story.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>並有多達8名球員遭到起訴並終身禁賽。<ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk"/>而身為捕手的沙爾克，自然也逃不過追查。但是沙爾克在世界大賽的打擊率高達3成04，而且在比賽中並沒有明顯的放水行為。<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ijMDAAAAMBAJ&q=ray+schalk+baseball+digest&pg=PA4 |title=Warm Up Tosses |author=Kuenster, John |date=September 1970 |work=Baseball Digest |access-date=12 January 2011 }}</ref>沙爾克後來也說到，球隊的兩大投手[[艾迪·席考特|艾迪·席考特]]和Lefty Williams常常忽略他的暗號，不按照他的配球策略投球。<ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk"/>幾年過後，沙爾克表示當時隊上另一位王牌先發投手[[瑞德·法伯|瑞德·法伯]]因為西班牙流感疫情肆虐而退出世界大賽，若他沒有退出，也許白襪隊不會輸球，放水的球員也不會因此被抓到。<ref name=TBT>{{cite book |title=The Team-by-Team Encyclopedia of Major League Baseball |url=https://archive.org/details/teambyteamencycl0000purd |last=Purdy |first=Dennis |year=2006 |publisher=[[Workman_Publishing_Company|Workman]] |location=New York City |isbn=0-7611-3943-5 }}</ref>

1920年，沙爾克的打擊率為2成70，打點數來到生涯新高的61分。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/>1922年，他接捕了[[查理·羅伯森|查理·羅伯森]]的完全比賽，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/boxscore/04301922.shtml |title=April 30, 1922 White Sox-Tigers box score |publisher=Baseball Almanac |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2020-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215173957/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/boxscore/04301922.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>並在兩個月後達成完全打擊。<ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk"/>最後他整年的打擊率為2成81，並敲出4轟與60分打點，並在MVP票選上拿下第三名。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1922.shtml#ALmvp |title=1922 American League Most Valuable Player Award voting |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2009-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090216191726/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1922.shtml#ALmvp |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1924年，由於手指受傷，<ref name="Ray Schalk, Veteran Catcher, Begins to Show Signs of Wear">{{cite news |title=Ray Schalk, Veteran Catcher, Begins to Show Signs of Wear |work=The Evening Tribune |page=6 |date=10 August 1924 |access-date=10 January 2011 |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=_dNcAAAAIBAJ&pg=1468,5034451&dq=ray+schalk&hl=en}}</ref>沙爾克的上場時間大幅減少，打擊率也掉到2成以下。<ref name="Ray Schalk, Veteran Catcher, Begins to Show Signs of Wear"/>1925年，沙爾克觸底反彈，整年打擊率為2成74，上壘率3成82為生涯新高。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/>1926年底，沙爾克接替了[[艾迪·柯林斯|艾迪·柯林斯]]的總教練工作。<ref>{{cite news |title=Ray Schalk New Chicago Pilot |agency=Associated Press |work=The Youngstown Vindicator |page=14 |date=12 November 1926 |access-date=10 January 2011 |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ECVAAAAAIBAJ&pg=3074,2630341&dq=ray+schalk&hl=en}}</ref>這也導致他從1927年起上場時間更加減少。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/managers/schalra01.shtml |title=Ray Schalk managing record |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2021-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523035808/https://www.baseball-reference.com/managers/schalra01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>1929年，他加入了巨人隊，僅出賽5場比賽後宣布退休。<ref name="Ray Schalk at Baseball Reference"/><ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk"/>
==晚年==
[[File:Ray_Schalk_plaque_HOF.jpg|right]]
退休後，他在小熊隊擔任兩年教練，之後又在小聯盟執教6年。<ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk"/><ref name="Ray Schalk minor league managing record">{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=schalk001ray#standard_managing::none |title=Ray Schalk minor league managing record |publisher=Baseball Reference |access-date=12 January 2011 |archive-date=2015-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527010837/http://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=schalk001ray#standard_managing::none |dead-url=no }}</ref>1944年，他成為小熊隊的球探。隨後他加入[[普渡大學|普渡大學]]，成為其棒球隊的助理教練，一直到他72歲退休為止。<ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk"/>1955年，名人堂資深委員會將他引薦入選名人堂。<ref>{{cite news |title=Home Run Baker And Ray Schalk Are Named To Hall Of Fame |agency=Associated Press |work=The Daytona Beach Morning Journal |page=11 |date=1 February 1955 |access-date=15 January 2011 |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xnE0AAAAIBAJ&pg=2641,107658&dq=ray+schalk&hl=en}}</ref>[[1959年世界大賽|1959年世界大賽]]，白襪睽違40年再度闖進世界大賽。他和另一名白襪傳奇選手[[瑞德·法伯|瑞德·法伯]]還一同受邀參加開球。<ref name="The Baseball Biography Project: Ray Schalk"/>1970年5月19日，沙爾克因癌症去世，享年78歲。<ref name="Chisox Great Ray Schalk Dead At 78">{{cite news |title=Chisox Great Ray Schalk Dead At 78 |agency=Associated Press |work=The Spokesman-Review |page=15 |date=20 May 1970 |access-date=15 January 2011 |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ipApAAAAIBAJ&pg=6753,1747684&dq=ray+schalk&hl=en}}</ref>
